    Summary table for comparative analysis between two numeric variables

    stat_two_num.Rd

    Create a summary table with t.test: statistic, p-value and IC(95%).

    Usage

    stat_two_num(df, grp_var, num_vars, method = "auto")

    Arguments

    df

    A single data.frame

    grp_var

    A character variable from a data.frame

    num_vars

    One or more variables from a data.frame

    method

    Method of summary and test (default = 'auto')

    Value

    A gt table.

    Examples

    
set.seed(123);df <-
 data.frame(
   grp_var = sample(paste("group", letters[1:2]),size = 10,replace = TRUE),
   num_var1 = rnorm(10),
   num_var2 = rpois(10,2)
 )

stat_two_num(df,grp_var,c(num_var1,num_var2),method = c("auto"))
